### Try to create an INVALID book (negative stock) — should FAIL with 400
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books
Content-Type: application/json

{ "ID": "103", "title": "Bad Book", "stock": -5 }

### Create a VALID book — should succeed
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books
Content-Type: application/json

{ "ID": "104", "title": "Foundation", "stock": 7 }